hopobject.body: I saw your advert in the paper ciprofloxacin 500 mg good for sinus infection Sansom - who is 41 and hails originally from Kent - is delighted to be inheriting the formidable legacy Featherstone built between the company's inception in 2006 and her recent departure. "So much of the hard work of imagining what the National Theatre of Scotland should be and how it should work has now been done", he says. "The reputation of the company is extraordinary, both nationally and internationally. I'm in a really enviable position."
